abstract: American consular officials visiting the West Bank are besieged by Jewish settlers throwing stones at them; officials are part of an investigation into claims of damage to Palestinian agricultural property.
lead_paragraph: Jewish settlers threw stones at American consular officials on Friday during a visit the officials made to the West Bank, Israeli police and Palestinian witnesses said.
